com.ephesoft.gxt.uploadbatch.client.i18n

Interface UploadBatchConstants

  • All Superinterfaces:
    LocaleCommonConstants

    public interface UploadBatchConstants
extends LocaleCommonConstants
    The class is used to define all the constants used in the Upload Batch module and support internationalization.
